NOTICE: Arena Allocator Components

The Arena Allocator (include/db25/memory/arena.hpp and src/memory/arena.cpp)
is marked as FROZEN CODE and requires a formal design change process for any
modifications. See include/db25/memory/FROZEN_DO_NOT_MODIFY.md for details.

Performance Baseline Requirements:
- Allocation latency: < 10ns
- Throughput: > 150M ops/s  
- Memory efficiency: > 85%
- Test coverage: > 98%

